Package com.fincons.message_viewer.net

This package provides a set of classes to implement network aspects related to the WebSocket used to present the received data

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WsSocket
    This interface provides the method to send the messages to all the active Web Sockets
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Listener
    This class provides methods for receiving notification events about ServletContext lifecycle changes.
    Message  
    MyEndpointConfigurator
    This class extends the ServerEndpointConfig.Configurator class to provide custom configuration algorithms.
    WsSocketDecryptedMessage
    This class declares the web socket endpoint on which the decrypted messages will be sent starting the standard CP-ABE/AES decryption process, defining the URL where this endpoint will be published at, and other important properties of the endpoint to the websocket runtime.
    WsSocketEncryptedMessage
    This class declares the web socket endpoint on which the encrypted message will be sent without starting the decryption process See the class WsSocketDecryptedMessage for more details about the methods implemented in this class.
